<paragraph id="IFRS09_IE109" base="F32824264"><paranum>IE109</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRSÂ 9"/><data name="paranum" value="IE109"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS09_P2295">Bank A reclassifies the portfolio of bonds out of the amortised cost measurement category and into the fair value through profit or loss measurement category. At the reclassification date, the portfolio of bonds is measured at fair value. Any gain or loss arising from a difference between the previous amortised cost amount of the portfolio of bonds and the fair value of the portfolio of bonds is recognised in profit or loss on reclassification.</p><table id="IFRS09_TAB0022" base="SL32827847" frame="all" orient="port"><tgroup cols="3"><colspec colnum="1" colname="C1" colwidth="64*" colsep="1" rowsep="1" align="left"/><colspec colnum="2" colname="C2" colwidth="18*" colsep="1" rowsep="1" align="left"/><colspec colnum="3" colname="C3" colwidth="18*" colsep="1" rowsep="1" align="left"/><thead><row><entry colname="C1"> <p id="IFRS09_P2296" typeface="sansserif"/></entry><entry colname="C2" align="right"> <p id="IFRS09_P2297" typeface="sansserif">Debit</p></entry><entry colname="C3" align="right"> <p id="IFRS09_P2298" typeface="sansserif">Credit</p></entry></row></thead><tbody><row><entry colname="C1" align="left" valign="top"> <p id="IFRS09_P2299" typeface="sansserif">Bonds (FVPL assets)</p></entry><entry colname="C2" align="right" valign="top"> <p id="IFRS09_P2300" typeface="sansserif">CU490,000</p></entry><entry colname="C3"> <p id="IFRS09_P2301" typeface="sansserif"/></entry></row><row><entry colname="C1" align="left" valign="top"> <p id="IFRS09_P2302" typeface="sansserif">Bonds (gross carrying amount of the amortised cost assets)</p></entry><entry colname="C2"> <p id="IFRS09_P2303" typeface="sansserif"/></entry><entry colname="C3" align="right" valign="top"> <p id="IFRS09_P2304" typeface="sansserif">CU500,000</p></entry></row><row><entry colname="C1" align="left" valign="top">